  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Housekeeping Staff",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Mama Shelter is a global lifestyle brand that blends hospitality, creativity, and community. Our hotels are vibrant hubs where guests feel at home, and every detail contributes to unforgettable experiences. Mama Shelter Singapore is the newest addition, bringing bold design and warm service to the city.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for dedicated and detail-oriented Housekeeping Staff to join our team. If you take pride in creating clean, welcoming spaces and enjoy working in a lively environment, this role is for you.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Clean and maintain guest rooms to ensure hygiene and presentation meet Mama Shelter standards</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and order in public areas and back-of-house spaces to support guest satisfaction</li><li>Identify and report maintenance issues promptly to ensure timely resolution and safety</li><li>Assist with laundry and linen management to maintain adequate supplies and quality</li><li>Provide friendly and professional service to guests when needed to enhance their experience</li><li>Work independently and collaborate with team members to complete daily housekeeping tasks efficiently</li><li>Adapt to shift schedules including weekends and holidays to support hotel operations</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Previous housekeeping or cleaning experience</li><li>Strong attention to detail to ensure thorough cleaning and presentation</li><li>Ability to work efficiently both independently and as part of a team</li><li>Positive attitude and commitment to delivering excellent guest service</li><li>Flexibility to work various shifts, including weekends and holidays</li></ul>",
